title: Governance decentralization [Exclude DEV/unlock INC wallets]
body:
Hello,

In the past, one of the votes was conditioned by a development wallet.
The idea is that governance is decentralized and governed by the community without internal influence of the project.
The proposal is to exclude any type of Unlock / developer wallet from the snapshot/DAO voting.
Example:
https://snapshot.org/#/unlock-protocol.eth/proposal/QmR8s9jvvJ82Mx8Ub1J5ESWFadwjjKtRpGs3vmCHbsqWUi

Thanks.
Regards,
author: 0x0235545F679B133543607C66988d60D772c10D4F
